        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer971131673" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3181456373902625668">What an unusual piece of history! This is a straight forward academic history of a little town in Michigan named Covert where free blacks and whites lived side by side. Why did such an integrated town survive and thrive in the time right after the Civil War? I think it&apos;s because a certain number of people there, black and white, had the integrity, skill, and character to make it so.</span>
  <span id="freeText3181456373902625668" style="display:none">What an unusual piece of history! This is a straight forward academic history of a little town in Michigan named Covert where free blacks and whites lived side by side. Why did such an integrated town survive and thrive in the time right after the Civil War? I think it's because a certain number of people there, black and white, had the integrity, skill, and character to make it so.</span>
