              <span id="reviewTextContainer694775861" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13894892498989964647">A remarkable book about an even more remarkable community in Michigan. This is the story of the town of Covert, Michigan, where black and white lived in harmony, before and during the Civil War Years. I had the pleasure of meeting the author of this book, when she came to our library on a tour of Michigan&apos;s Notable books. Her book evolved from her graduate work, and she was passionate about the story of this unusual town. </span>
  <span id="freeText13894892498989964647" style="display:none">A remarkable book about an even more remarkable community in Michigan. This is the story of the town of Covert, Michigan, where black and white lived in harmony, before and during the Civil War Years. I had the pleasure of meeting the author of this book, when she came to our library on a tour of Michigan's Notable books. Her book evolved from her graduate work, and she was passionate about the story of this unusual town. </span>
  <a data-text-id="13894892498989964647" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


