<span id="freeTextContainer14724482728739502165">I really enjoyed this book. I probably should have only given it a three because I would not re read it or anything but I wouldn&apos;t want someone to not read it for the rating reason. It is more the subject matter that might not appeal to someone as it deals with the history of blacks in America from the Civil war forward. I found it very interesting and eyeopening on a number of fronts.</span>
